data.description: The main level of this extraordinary home boasts an open floor plan, while upstairs you'll find 3 Bedrooms, a Tech Niche, and 2.5 Baths. Additionally, there is a delightful Deck off the Master suite upstairs that you can relish. Located near parks, sports complexes, and dog park you'll enjoy all this turn key home has to offer.
